<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
  <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="Aink205-kilavi"> notumalar varaivu vēṇṭi viṭṭuḻit talaimakaṭkuḷatākiya varuttam nōkki ivaḷ ivvāṟātaṟkuk kāraṇam eṉṉai yeṉṟu viṉaviya cevilikkut tōḻi aṟattoṭu niṉṟatu.</p>

      <p xml:lang="en"> The confidante standing up with virtue to the foster-mother, who asked, “What is the reason for her to become this way?” regarding the suffering of the heroine, as the stranger, desiring marriage, left. </p>
      </div>
    
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink205">
<l>aṉṉāy vāḻivēṇ ṭaṉṉaiyeṉ ṟōḻi</l>
<l>naṉinā ṇuṭaiya ṇiṉṉu mañcu</l>
<l>moliveḷ ḷaruvi yōṅkumalai nāṭaṉ</l>
<l>malarnta mārpiṟ pāyaṟ</l>
<l>ṟuñciya veyya ṇōkō yāṉē</l>
      </lg>
  
<lg xml:lang="en">
          <l>Oh Mother, please Mother, </l>
          <l>my friend, profoundly shy, is even afraid of you.  </l>
          <l rend="space indent">She yearns to sleep on the bed of the blossomed chest </l>
          <l rend="indent">of the man from the land of lofty mountains </l>
          <l rend="indent">with resounding white waterfalls.</l>
          <l rend="space">Ah, I ache!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
